      <scopecontent id="aspace_8e05aaa21d6e39ccb37b7afbc5f0eca2">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection is comprised of thirteen scrapbooks compiled by Lawrence Gordon of Durban, South Africa, an engineer and collector of Africana. The scrapbooks are filled with clippings primarily of political cartoons from South African and English newspapers and journals. The clippings are arranged in loose chronological order and they cover a variety of subjects.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
